{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/minimal-theme-slideshow-on-product-pages-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":618,"date":"2021-03-27T06:12:23","date_gmt":"2021-03-27T06:12:23","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=618"},"modified":"2021-05-09T00:03:58","modified_gmt":"2021-05-09T00:03:58","slug":"minimal-theme-slideshow-on-product-pages-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/minimal-theme-slideshow-on-product-pages-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Minimal Theme: add a slideshow to your product pages"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>One of the best things about the minimal theme is its particularly elegant simplicity. However, in one specific area that its simplicity fails to deliver is at the product page; lacking a proper way to present images can be a deal breaker for the pickiest customers. Constantly clicking between thumbnails and then scrolling up to see the new image doesn&#8217;t feel like the most UX friendly approach.<br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll show you how you can quick and easily add a slideshow to your Minimal theme product page, all it takes is copying and pasting one single code file. You can <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://acid-tests.myshopify.com/products/dummy-product\" target=\"_blank\">view the end result clicking here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-current-theme\">Making a backup of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-files\">Downloading the files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/minimal-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Download</strong></a><strong> </strong>the files <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/minimal-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\">clicking here.</a> (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://acid-tests.myshopify.com/products/dummy-product\" target=\"_blank\">live preview</a>)<br><br>The complete details about the slideshow <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/minimal-theme-slider-pro\" target=\"_blank\">can be found clicking here.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-installing-the-slideshow-code\">Installing the slideshow code </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Actions&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1349\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-626\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code.jpg 1349w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-600x273.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-1200x546.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/edit-code-768x350.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1349px) 100vw, 1349px\" /></li><li>Find a file named <strong>product-template.liquid</strong><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1004\" height=\"417\" class=\"wp-image-628\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template.jpg 1004w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template-600x249.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/product-template-768x319.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1004px) 100vw, 1004px\" /></li><li>Delete everything inside of this file. Make sure it is blank:<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1265\" height=\"548\" class=\"wp-image-630\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1.jpg 1265w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-600x260.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-1200x520.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/blank1-768x333.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1265px) 100vw, 1265px\" /></li><li>Now, inside of the .zip you downloaded, there will be a file called <strong>product-template.txt</strong>. Copy all the code inside of this file.</li><li>Paste this code you copied into <strong>product-template.liquid</strong> and save.</li><li>That is it! Your slideshow is now working and ready to use.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-customizing-your-new-slideshow-to-your-liking\">Customizing your new slideshow to your liking</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>In your Shopify admin, navigate to&nbsp;<strong>Online Store</strong>&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;<strong>Themes&nbsp;</strong>&gt;<strong>Customize</strong>.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1699\" height=\"751\" class=\"wp-image-570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg\" alt=\"Accessing the customize page on Shopify admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123.jpg 1699w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-600x265.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1200x530.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-768x339.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/customize123-1536x679.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" /></li><li>On the top, from the dropdown options, select <strong>product pages</strong>. <br><br>Once this page loads, click on <strong>product pages</strong> on the left.<br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"804\" height=\"485\" class=\"wp-image-632\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1.jpg 804w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1-600x362.jpg 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/prod1-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 804px) 100vw, 804px\" /></li><li>Inside the <strong>Product pages</strong> menu you&#8217;ll find all available options for the Minimal Slider.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-something-went-wrong-there-is-a-bug-or-i-can-t-install-it\">Something went wrong, there is a bug or I can&#8217;t install it</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll be more than happy to help you out. <br><br>Just please send us an email at <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> with your website URL and we&#8217;ll get back to you on the same day to assist you and get it installed.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to add a rich slideshow to your product pages in just a few minutes. More than 20 customizable features built-in.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":637,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[243],"acf":[],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/MinimalSlider-600x338.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/MinimalSlider-100x100.png","featured_image_lar